commit.message:
Add output typemaps for cdtext_list_languages_v2() and cdtext_get()

This results in cdtext_list_languages_v2() returning List[int] and
cdtext_get() returning Union[None, bytes], whih can be interpreted
directly in python.

Imprive iso2.py when there is an error

iso1.py: don't translate filenames in ISO9660

Wrong file name in iso2.py example

Case matters.

Fixes #1

Remove legacy 0.8{2,3} libcdio code

libcdio before 2.0.0 really doesn't exist anymore
